:

*"On je ostavio svoju porodicu kada je napustio zemlju." (He left his family when he left the country.)

*"Čovek se nije ostavio zaplašiti od teške situacije." (The man did not let himself be intimidated by the difficult situation.)

*"Ona je ostavila kuću i otišla u inostranstvo." (She left the house and went abroad.)

*"On je ostao bez para kada je ostavio posao." (He was left without money when he left the job.)

*"Ona je ostavila svoj stari život iza sebe." (She left her old life behind her.)